Reference audio must be provided as a paired .wav + .txt file placed in the ComfyUI/input directory.
The two files must share the same filename.
Restart ComfyUI after adding files.

nodes.title: Sample Text to Record
widgets_values: This is a test recording to make AI clone my voice.

Step 1: Press and hold the green “Press and Hold to Record” button and read the Sample text to record aloud.
Step 2: Enter the text you want to generate in F5-TTS Audio from input.
Step 3: Run the workflow to generate audio in your own voice.
Hello everyone, today is Monday, and this is a test of my cloned voice.
